        'B1' => [
            ['How does art enrich our lives?', 'Art gives us new ways to see the world and to feel understood. A song can capture an emotion I couldn\'t articulate, and a film can show me a life I\'ll never live. Art expands empathy and makes ordinary moments feel meaningful.', 'Explain with examples + effect.', ['articulate', 'empathy', 'meaningful', 'expand']],
            ['Describe a book or film that changed your perspective.', 'A novel called "The Kite Runner" changed how I think about guilt and friendship. It showed me how the past haunts us and how redemption is possible. I finished it and saw my own relationships differently.', 'Use narrative + reflection.', ['guilt', 'redemption', 'haunt', 'perspective']],
            ['Do you think traditional arts are dying out?', 'Some are struggling, but others are being reinvented. Younger artists blend traditional forms with modern styles, which keeps them alive. The threat is real, but so is the creativity of those keeping traditions going in new ways.', 'Acknowledge threat + note adaptation.', ['reinvent', 'blend', 'threat', 'creativity']],
            ['How important is it to preserve cultural heritage?', 'Vitally important. Heritage connects us to our roots and gives us identity in a fast-changing world. But preservation shouldn\'t mean freezing culture — the best heritage evolves while keeping its core. We honour the past by keeping it meaningful today.', 'Balance preservation with evolution.', ['heritage', 'identity', 'freeze', 'evolve']],
            ['What role does music play in your life?', 'Music is a daily companion. It matches my moods — calm music when I\'m stressed, upbeat songs when I need energy. Going to live concerts is one of my favourite experiences because the shared energy is electric.', 'Describe personal + social functions.', ['companion', 'mood', 'upbeat', 'electric']],
            ['Should the government fund the arts?', 'I believe so. The arts enrich society but often can\'t survive on profit alone. Public funding lets risky, experimental work exist and makes culture accessible to everyone, not just those who can pay. A society that funds the arts invests in its soul.', 'Argue with reasons + metaphor.', ['fund', 'experimental', 'accessible', 'soul']],
